PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784213293
OL,3,CZoo gets new capybara as search for
OL,4,Cmissing Samba continues
OL,6,FThe zoo said in a statement that it
OL,7,Farranged for Ripple's transfer to
OL,8,Fensure Tango's "continued welfare by
OL,9,Fproviding her with appropriate
OL,10,Fcompanionship".
OL,12,F"We know many people will be wondering
OL,13,Fabout Samba," the statement read.
OL,15,F"Welcoming Ripple does not mean we
OL,16,Fhave stopped searching for her. Our
OL,17,Fefforts to find Samba continue, and
OL,18,Fher welfare remains a priority for the
OL,19,Fteam."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/3
